It's here! The Titan Ultimate Hair Health Package: HAIR HEALTH CAPSULES, INJECTABLE BIOTIN, & REVITALIZING HAIR FOAM! 

HAIR HEALTH CAPSULES:
Our Titan hair health capsules have methionine, acetylcysteine, saw palmetto, biotin, histidine, grape seed and nettle leaf. These are a great solution for helping to grow back or strengthen your hair and nails. This capsule can also help with getting back that glowing skin. 

INJECTABLE BIOTIN:
Biotin is a B-complex vitamin, also known as B7 or Vitamin H. Biotin is necessary for the cell growth and the production of fatty acids in living organisms.
Biotin shots are great for growing and strengthening hair, skin, and nails. This is a vitamin that we usually do not get enough of in our food consumption. Biotin can also help turn the carbs, fats, and proteins in the food you eat into energy to fuel your body. 

Titan Revitalizer Hair Foam:
This therapy may help treat, prevent, and reverse hair thinning and loss for males & females! We all know that hair loss is a common sign of aging, stress and hormonal imbalances but it can often make us feel self-conscious and anxious that the shedding may get worse. Many males and females have hair loss or thinning do due to AGA (Androgenic Alopecia). 

Key ingredients: Minoxidil, Finasteride, & Latanoprost
Minoxidil is a vasodilator that widens blood vessels and opens potassium channels, thereby allowing for more oxygen, blood and nutrients to reach the hair follicle. It is used to increase new hair growth in cases of hereditary hair loss. When applied to the scalp, this medicine can promote hair growth in men with male pattern baldness. This medicine can also help women with thin hair and frontal hair loss. 

Finasteride works by lowering the overall amount of DHT ( Dihydrotestosterone) in the body. It accomplishes this by blocking the formation of DHT. Once levels of this hormone are lowered, hair follicles will stop or slow degeneration. It has been shown to be extremely effective at preventing and slowing the loss of hair. In some cases it will stimulate significant new hair growth.

There are dozens of potential health benefits of IGF-1 therapy based on preliminary research results. Patients may experience some or all of these health benefits after they start their therapy:
Increased muscle mass and strength
Faster workout recovery times
Faster injury healing times
Increased energy levels
Increased exercise stamina
Increased bone density
Improved skin tone
Better sleep quality
Helps regulate fat for use as energy, resulting in fat loss.

Modified form of amino acids 176-191 of the GH polypeptide

AOD 9604 works by mimicking the way natural growth hormone regulates fat metabolism but without the adverse effects on blood sugar or growth that is seen with unmodified growth hormone. AOD 9604 stimulates lipolysis (the breakdown or destruction of fat) and inhibits lipogenesis (the transformation of nonfat food materials into body fat).

AOD 9604 has no effect on serum IGF-1 levels!

Recent findings have shown, in addition to it's fat loss properties, AOD 9604 processes many other regenerative properties associated with growth hormone. Currently trials are underway to show the application of AOD 9604 in osteoarthritis, hypercholesterolemia as well as possible bone and cartilage repair.

DSIP (Delta Sleep‐Inducing Peptide)
DSIP (Delta sleep-inducing peptide) is a well-known neuromodulator & natural sleep-promoting nonapeptide with many other physiologic functions. It is typically found in the brain & easily passes the blood-brain barrier. It has been discovered & heavily studied for over 40 years. It has been used for the treatment of poor sleep, pain conditions, stress-related symptoms, low testosterone (via stimulation of LH), & even sometimes as an antioxidant.

SLEEP:
DSIP has been described as a sleep-promoting substance rather than a sedative. There is a modulating effect on sleep & wake functions with greater activity in circumstances where sleep is disturbed. There are essentially 5 stages of sleep, these can be broken down into 2 categories REM & NREM sleep. These translate to Rapid Eye Movement & Non-Rapid Eye movement sleep. The problem with many sleep aids is that they change the time or duration of these sleep cycles. The problem with this is these cycles are ALL associated with important physiological processes & anabolic hormone production. DSIP does not change these sleep stages. It increases the ability to go to sleep & offers a more restful sleep.

BENEFITS OF DSIP:
- Can restore disturbed sleep patterns
- Can promote LH & GH release
- Can reduce persistent/chronic pain
- Can modulate cortisol production

AOD 9604 PEPTIDE WEIGHT LOSS THERAPY
is a modified form of amino acids 176-191 of the GH polypeptide.
AOD 9604 works by mimicking the way natural growth hormone regulates fat metabolism but without the adverse effects on blood sugar or growth that is seen with unmodified growth hormone. AOD 9604 stimulates lipolysis (the breakdown or destruction of fat) and inhibits lipogenesis (the transformation of nonfat food materials into body fat).
AOD 9604 has no effect on serum IGF-1 levels!
Recent findings have shown, in addition to it's fat loss properties, AOD 9604 processes many other regenerative properties associated with growth hormone. Currently trials are underway to show the application of AOD 9604 in osteoarthritis, hypercholesterolemia as well as possible bone and cartilage repair.
(This therapy also comes in an oral format as well)
